* 喬哈夏希曾經說他在美國見了[[耶穌|耶穌]].<ref name=GoharJesus>{{cite web|title=Return of Lord Jesus: Lord Jesus meets Lord Gohar Shahi in America|url=http://www.goharshahi.us/index.php?/about/meeting-with-jesus/|accessdate=1 July 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522005656/http://www.goharshahi.us/index.php?%2Fabout%2Fmeeting-with-jesus%2F|archivedate=2013年5月22日}} 
</ref>
* 夏希的支持者曾說他的肖像有出現在[[月亮|月亮]]，[[太陽|太陽]]，[[星雲星|星雲星]]和麥加的黑石.<ref name="hrrpt">{{cite web|url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2000/sa/710.htm|title=Country Reports on Human Rights Practices by United States of America|publisher=[[U.S._Department_of_State|U.S. Department of State]]|date=23 February 2003|accessdate=7 March 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080614111537/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2000/sa/710.htm|archive-date=2008-06-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title =Divine Signs| url = http://www.goharshahi.us/divine-signs/| accessdate = 16 July 2013}}</ref>

